headline: Novo Nordisk Dives As Ozempic Fails To Slow Alzheimer's; Lilly Falls, Biogen Jumps
summary: Novo Nordisk reported Monday that a Ozempic pill failed to slow the progression of Alzheimer's in two big studies. Novo dived, Eli Lilly fell. Biogen rose.
